Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.data_spec

Enum Commands

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Commands>
uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.data_spec.Commands
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Commands>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Commands
extends Enum<Commands>
Set of opcodes for the spec executor. All names come from the Data Specification specification document.
